        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-08-14 18:25:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe fix is definitely present in upstream source and has been for a long time.\nAs far as I can tell SuSE doesn't pick it up in a release until 11.4 at the earliest,",
